                        <interp inst="t18450512-name-975" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY JORDAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a butcher. I was at the fair—I saw Manyon feel the prosecutor's coat-tail pocket—Marooney was standing by his side.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Marooney's Defence.</hi> I did not know this boy, only I thought I had seen him; I asked if he lived in such a place, and if he was going home; that was all I said to him.</p>
